org.eclipse.jst.ws.jaxws.dom.runtime.provider
Interface IEndpointMetadata

public interface IEndpointMetadata

Represents metadata for an endpoint. Contains information about the name and namespace of the endpoint. Contains exposed operations. This interface is intended to be used as input data for implementors of IEndpointGenerator.

Author:
Plamen Pavlov
